<p>Download PostgreSQL from the Postgresapp.</p>

<ol>
  <li>Visit the <a href="https://postgresapp.com/downloads.html">postgresapp homepage</a> and download the latest version of Postgres.app</li>
  <li>Open the downloaded file and drag it into your applications folder</li>
  <li>Open your applications and open the app
    <ul>
      <li>If you get a message around â€œâ€˜Postgresâ€™ canâ€™t be opened because the identity of the developer cannot be confirmed.â€, make sure that you are opening the app from inside your applications folder.</li>
