<h2 id="install-postico">Install Postico</h2>

<p>https://eggerapps.at/postico/</p>

<p>This is a tool that will make it much easier to navigate your local databases and build/run SQL commands.</p>

<h2 id="install-chrome">Install Chrome</h2>

<p>If you are currently using another browser, download and install Chrome <a href="https://www.google.com/chrome/">here</a>. This will make it so that we can share shortcuts and have a consistent experience when debugging together as a class.</p>
